2013;;Shotgun Wedding;;American;;Danny Roew;;Mike Damus, Kim Shaw, Joel McKinnon Miller;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shotgun_Wedding_(2013_film);;While drunk, Robert (Mike Damus), the groom-to-be, 'accidentally' shoots the maid of honor of his fiance in the face during a skeet-shooting event, and his scheming mother does whatever needed to ensure the wedding will occur, even to conspire with her ex-husband or kidnap the maid of honor.[2]